<template>

        <v-layout>

                <WebsiteCard  v-for="website in websitesData" :key="website.alias" v-bind:website="website"></WebsiteCard>

        </v-layout>

</template>

<script>
    import WebsiteCard from "./WebsiteCard";
    export default {
        name: "Home",
        components: {WebsiteCard},
        props: ["websitesData"]

    }
</script>

<style scoped>
    .bold {
        font-weight: bold !important;
    }
</style>
